    "Analysis on αWe conducted a analysis on the learning α used in our projected sign gradient ascent.",
    "We experimented with α values of 1, 2, and 4 across five different prompts (P1 to P5) and two Stable Diffusion models (SD14 and SD15).",
    "IX presents the results of this study.",
    "As shown in Tab.",
    "IX, α = 2 generally yields the best performance across most prompts and metrics."
